tion and with labyrinth-like morphology of the Sn, we observe a\nquite different behavior: the superconducting state has a microwave response\nsimilar to the thicker, completely covering films with low microwave losses;\nbut the metallic state of these Sn films is so lossy that resonator operation\nis suppressed completely.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Feb 2016 10:30:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 12:10:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-01"}
